he end of section 2 for exercise: https://github.com/ggelashvili/learnphptherightway-project/tree/2.33\n\nCHAPTERS\n00:00 - Autoloading\n05:52 - PSR\n10:27 - Composer & dependency management\n16:31 - Autoloading using composer', '00:00:00', 'rqzYdHdyMH0', 'video/youtube', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rqzYdHdyMH0/mqdefault.jpg', '(min-width: 400px;)', 'image/jpeg', 'UCNoeG15U4pLBrFVHTw3xByw', '2021-03-19 04:52:09', 3, '2022-11-11 11:51:33', '2022-11-11 11:51:33');
